text: Yelena Kalugina (born 22 May 1972) is a Belarusian cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:People from Nolinsky District Category:Belarusian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Belarus Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics
